			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1289228">
									

<p>I like this a lot, actually. It's sometimes easy to forget that some of these things have very human wants and needs. yes, it sucks to be a &quot;ward&quot; of The Foundation&#8230;but you're also provided for, not (generally) shot at, and not stared at over-much.</p>
